en.description: The Sybaris Prime is the Prime variant of the Sybaris burst-fire rifle. Released alongside Oberon Prime and Silva & Aegis Prime, it features the highest base damage of all the Sybaris variants and is geared towards inflicting Status Effects.
en.codex: Become judge, jury, and executioner with this elegant and deadly lever-action Tenno rifle capable of firing a twin pair of bullets in quick succession.

ru.description: Холеный и грациозный, золотой символ превосходства Тенно.
